org.apache.avalon.repository
Interface ArtifactDatabase

All Known Subinterfaces:
Repository
All Known Implementing Classes:
ArtifactDatabaseImpl, DefaultFileRepository
public interface ArtifactDatabase

Manages relational information associated with artifact attributes within the repository presuming some attributes can be multivalued while others are single valued.

Version:
$Revision: 1.1 $
Author:
Alex Karasulu, $Author: mcconnell $
